"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 23, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104exe1665702665391.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/exe1665702665391.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/exe1665702665391.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"exe1665702665391\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $variation\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"exe1665702665391___variation_300743\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return or specify the name of the library containing objects needed by the application or component.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"exe1665702665391__topic_d91484e1_d91485e1_d91486e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exe1665702665391__p_d91487e1_d91488e1_d91489e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$variation</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exe1665702665391__p_d91490e1_d91491e1_d91492e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$variation</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"exe1665702665391__section_w1579ab1b7b5_w1580ab1b7_w1581ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exe1665702665391__p_d91493e1_d91494e1_d91495e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$variation = \"ACME\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"exe1665702665391__topic_d60907e1_d60908e1_d60909e1_d60910e1_d60911e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d808242e87\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exe1665702665391__p_d91499e1_d91500e1_d91501e1\">Name of the current library.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"exe1665702665391__topic_d60912e1_d60913e1_d60914e1_d60915e1_d60916e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d808242e96\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exe1665702665391__d6006e20\">Allowed in Form, Report, and Service components, but not in self-contained components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"exe1665702665391__topic_d60917e1_d60918e1_d60919e1_d60920e1_d60921e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d808242e106\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exe1665702665391__p_d91511e1_d91512e1_d91513e1\">The value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$variation</span> determines the library used to locate the following resources at runtime:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"exe1665702665391__li_d36131e1_d36132e1_d36133e1\">Messages\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"exe1665702665391__li_d36134e1_d36135e1_d36136e1\">Help texts\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"exe1665702665391__li_d36137e1_d36138e1_d36139e1\">Menus\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"exe1665702665391__li_d36140e1_d36141e1_d36142e1\">Panels\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"exe1665702665391__li_d36143e1_d36144e1_d36145e1\">Glyphs\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"exe1665702665391__li_d36146e1_d36147e1_d36148e1\">Device translation tables\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"exe1665702665391__li_d36149e1_d36150e1_d36151e1\">Keyboard translation tables\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"exe1665702665391__li_d36152e1_d36153e1_d36154e1\">Language setups\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exe1665702665391__p_d91514e1_d91515e1_d91516e1\">It overrides the value set by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$VARIATION</span> assignment setting, but not the library specified by the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Library</span> property of the application shell or component. This cannot be changed without recompiling the component or application shell.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exe1665702665391__p_d91517e1_d91518e1_d91519e1\">Changing the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$variation</span> does not affect the global ProcScript and global variables used at application run time.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fcq1665703251101.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$VARIATION</a><p>Specify the library name for global objects needed by the application when the application starts. Libraries are typed, so each global object library can have the same name which functions as a shared namespace which can be specified by this setting.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sdn1665703008210.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$language</a><p>Return or set the current language code used for language-related global objects and language setups.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527373\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527373\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$variation Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 23, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $variation Return or specify the name of the library containing objects needed by the application or component. $variation $variation = String Example: $variation = \"ACME\" Return Values Name of the current library. Use Allowed in Form, Report, and Service components, but not in self-contained components. Description The value of $variation determines the library used to locate the following resources at runtime: Messages Help texts Menus Panels Glyphs Device translation tables Keyboard translation tables Language setups It overrides the value set by the $VARIATION assignment setting, but not the library specified by the Library property of the application shell or component. This cannot be changed without recompiling the component or application shell. Changing the value of $variation does not affect the global ProcScript and global variables used at application run time. Related Links $VARIATION Specify the library name for global objects needed by the application when the application starts. Libraries are typed, so each global object library can have the same name which functions as a shared namespace which can be specified by this setting. $language Return or set the current language code used for language-related global objects and language setups. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}